description: Shi Hao lives to practice Taoism, cultivating himself to fight suffering and calamity. As a result of a catastrophe, his body turned into millions and millions of blood drops that rain down through the ages, getting refined through space and time. Tested in the endless flow of time, he transforms freely and eternally.
